# 📄 JSON Example (API Request + Config)

You can use this JSON either as a **config file** or **request payload example**:

```json
{
  "app": {
    "name": "Vishakha's AI Assistant",
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "description": "Simple AI chatbot using OpenAI API"
  },
  "api": {
    "endpoint": "https://api.openai.com/v1/chat/completions",
    "method": "POST",
    "headers": {
      "Content-Type": "application/json",
      "Authorization": "Bearer YOUR_API_KEY"
    }
  },
  "request_body": {
    "model": "gpt-4o-mini",
    "messages": [
      {
        "role": "system",
        "content": "You are a helpful assistant."
      },
      {
        "role": "user",
        "content": "hi how are you?"
      }
    ]
  },
  "ui": {
    "title": "Vishakha's AI Assistant",
    "input_placeholder": "Ask me anything...",
    "send_button": "Send"
  }
}
